A while back, I had the idea of
evacuating on the back of an Armu.

rows.label: qst701910_msg0002
rows.name:
But...Freja didn't have the strength
to hold onto it and fell off.

rows.label: qst701910_msg0003
rows.name: We have to do something to help her.

rows.label: qst701910_msg0004
rows.name:
But if Marco's medicine couldn't
help, what on Alst can we do?
